content.rendered:
Directed by Saagar K Chandra.

Written by Ravi Reddy Mallu.

Cast Nara Rohith(Imtiaz Ali). Sree Vishnu(Railway Raju). Tanya Hope(Nitya). Sasha Singh(Riya) . Ajay(Nadayar). Darbha Appaji Ambarisha(Riya’s father). Brahmaji(Vittal Seth). Manasa Himavarsha(Ahalya). Jeeva(IPS officer). Rajeev Kanakala(Ashok Reddy). Satyadev Kancharana(Praneeth Kumar). Padmaja Lanka(Mother). Raj Madiraju(IPS officer). G.V. Sudhakar Naidu(Baghwan Sas).Jabardasth Naveen. Sai Neeraj(Young Tester). Ravi Prakash(Railway Raju’s cricket coach). Satya Prakash(Purushottham). Jhansi Rathod(Cricketer). Srinivasa Reddy(Srinu). Sameer(Chief Cricket Selection Member). Prabhas Sreenu(Solomon).Taniya.Tnr. Ravi Varma(Savyasachi). Kittu Vissapragada(Lawyer)

Languages Telugu.

Producers Prashanti. Nara Rohith. Krishna Vijay.

Production Aran Media Works.
